{"tid":2394401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃務員入] 港共俾支槍你叫你係新屋嶺槍斃一個手足，你唔抆雞就炒你，你會點揀？","createTime":"2021-02-04T06:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T11:16:56.000Z","uid":55552,"like":5,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ddcdf1bb1d57c84812cc0e4b04dec49d7c272304","tid":2394401,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"比著我真係會抆雞，你諗下，就算你唔落手都大把人等住落手，你俾人炒分分鐘俾支那人乘虛而入，到時手足咪俾人折磨得仲慘，女手足俾人輪姦，男手足俾人雞姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋多啲黃務員留係政府，起碼手足俾人強姦少啲，又可以死得痛快啲，點都好過俾藍絲狗支那人同黑警折磨而死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最重要係，我抆雞，我起碼可以用份糧日日食黃店，用港共錢壯大黃圈，但如果我反抗，就乜都無，基本數學題，傻嘅都識揀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c7f075c6d8118112a4210c6027c1959cef6d3f","tid":2394401,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:56:13.000Z","msg":"False dilemma"},{"pid":"002013ab436f5e19a706fd14b772724f05f2b5f3","tid":2394401,"uid":74058,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:56:39.000Z","msg":"呢啲都係反抗空間嚟"},{"pid":"8413d7a908f0b20d03943b301a89ea3b106577d5","tid":2394401,"uid":241132,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"開槍, 之後收埋證據放連登"},{"pid":"307313be797677f2040a5cc6daf5f29e4125939b","tid":2394401,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4c7f075c6d8118112a4210c6027c1959cef6d3f","tid":2394401,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T06:56:13.000Z","msg":"False dilemma"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"港共話只可以二揀一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05bd60559adabaa052ad05a726035d9f607a3f5","tid":2394401,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"002013ab436f5e19a706fd14b772724f05f2b5f3","tid":2394401,"uid":74058,"like":1,"dislike":